      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4">
      <b class="emoji">
        3️
      </b>
      <h3 class="subheading">
        Instantly Organizes
      </h3>
      <p class="paragraph">
        Quiki categorizes captured Q&amp;A to create a searchable enterprise knowledge base
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h4>
    <!--Using NLP and machine learning algorithms trained on your company's data-->
  </h4>
